            "title": "香港數字債券發行上量 更多發行人料將繼續入場",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"香港數字債券發行上量 更多發行人料將繼續入場\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RLXQHOjqcGsiQKSvdk6TGA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-08/316700f0-854f-11f0-af37-5b587879a7dc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">香港數字債券發行上量 更多發行人料將繼續入場</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
