        {
            "title": "泰國議會即將選舉總理 保守派政治家阿奴廷勢將當選",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Anutin Charnvirakul Photographer: Dario Pignatelli/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HQ_mFWmamsFKHGi8IZupVA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/105ad9b0c729bb336ff4ac2e0a13c9b5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Anutin Charnvirakul Photographer: Dario Pignatelli/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 泰國保守派政治家阿努廷·參威拉恭勢將在周五被議會選舉為總理。此前他把保皇派和民主派令人難以置信地聯合起來，力圖打破政治僵局。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">議會下議院預計將於當地時間上午9時召集後開始投票。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿努廷的當選幾乎已成定局，勢將成為短短兩年多的時間裡泰國第三位總理。他已獲得492名下議院議員中289人的支持，遠高於獲得多數席位所需的247票。他的支持者包括議會最大政黨——進步派的人民黨。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">58歲的阿奴廷是泰自豪黨領導人，他的競爭者是猜甲森·尼提西裡，是為泰黨領導陣營的候選人，受到頗具影響力前總理他信·西那瓦的支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：泰國朝野雙方競相阻撓對方組閣 黨爭之亂愈演愈烈恐拖累經濟</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"阿努廷攝影師：Dario Pignatelli/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mlwh4SGyeqiDa9R7dw3HoQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/17f26c8d3429b6035b9c54f0b9f9534c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">阿努廷攝影師：Dario Pignatelli/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿奴廷此前曾在內閣中任職，經歷多個政府，從民粹主義者他信，到政變領導人巴育·占奧差，以及最近的佩通坦·欽那瓦政府。近十年來，他一直扮演著聯盟造王者的角色。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：他信突然離開泰國前往杜拜 正值議會即將選舉新總理</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Anutin Set to Win Thai Parliament Vote as Third PM in Two Years</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
